# Internationalization (i18n)

This project uses i18next for internationalization support.

## Key Files
- [i18n.ts](mdc:src/i18n.ts) - i18n configuration
- [i18n.d.ts](mdc:src/i18n.d.ts) - TypeScript type definitions for i18n

## Usage
- Language switching is handled by the [LanguageSwitcher.tsx](mdc:src/components/LanguageSwitcher.tsx) component
- Translations are stored in the `/src/locales` directory, with separate files for each language
- The application supports automatic language detection based on browser settings
